Install and use Font Awesome (icon) in i3 config

1. Go to https://github.com/FortAwesome/Font-Awesome/releases
2. Download the latest .zip file
3. uznip awesome.zip
4. cd that_new_folder/fonts
5. mkdir ~/.fonts
6. cp fontawesome.ttf ~/.fonts

7. Look at http://fontawesome.io/cheatsheet/ for copy and paste characters
8. Log out and log in for better renders :)
